N:Ireland, Sliabh Luachra region of the Cork-Kerry border. Standard tuning. AA'BB'. Source for notated version: accordion player Johnny O'Leary (Sliabh Luarchra region), recorded in recital at Na Píobairí Uilleann, February, 1981 [Moylan]. Bulmer & Sharpley (Music from Ireland), vol. 1, No. 73. Ceol, vol. 2, No. 4. Moylan (Johnny O'Leary), 1994; No. 61, pg. 35. Globestyle Irish CDORBD 085, Padraig O'Keeffe - "The Rushy Mountain" (1994. Reissue of Topic recordings). Shanachie 79022, "Chieftains #2." Topic 12T309, Padraig O'Keeffe, Denis Murphy & Julia Clifford - "Kerry Fiddles."

